<body>

<div1 type="letter">

<pb facs="nei.j4a.3.40"/>

<note type="signature">U Sinclair</note> 

<fw type="letterhead">

  UPTON SINCLAIR
<lb/>
  CROTON-ON-HUDSON, N. Y. 
<lb/>

  TELEPHONE CROTON 85

</fw>

<opener>
<dateline>August 22, 1914</dateline>


<salute>My dear Mr. Neihardt:</salute>
</opener>
<p>Many thanks for your kind letter. I will get the poems you mention.</p>
<closer>
<salute>Sincerely,</salute>

<signed>U Sinclair</signed> 
</closer>

</div1>
